Dynamic sidebox display template for SemanticSchemas categories.

Composes display-header, display-rows, render-reverse, and subobjects
into a floating sidebar layout.

Parameters:
* category - The category name (without namespace prefix)
* page - Target page to read property values from. Defaults to
         {{FULLPAGENAME}}.
* nested - Set to "yes" to suppress Backlinks + subobject sections
         (see Category/table for full rationale).
